secure-net-stack/
│
├─ README.md              # Overview and instructions
├─ LICENSE                # MIT License (open source friendly)
├─ .gitignore             # Ignores temporary or compiled files
├─ requirements.txt       # Python dependencies (cryptography)
│
├─ src/                   # Core source code modules
│   ├─ networking.py      # SecureSocket implementation
│   ├─ encryption.py      # SecureChannel implementation
│   └─ node.py            # NetworkNode integrating socket + encryption
│
├─ examples/              # Example usage scripts
│   └─ demo_node.py       # Demonstrates sending/receiving encrypted messages
│
├─ tests/                 # Unit tests for modules
│   ├─ test_networking.py
│   └─ test_encryption.py
│
└─ docs/                  # Documentation
    └─ architecture.md    # Architecture overview
